race.comment: Very even. GALLOPING GURU (1) is better than recent runs and looks well placed here. Comes back in journey but has the blinkers added and did place only other try this course. Will be prominent and give a sight. WHISPERING PHARAOH (2) placed two back then broke through last time in a BM56 scoring by a nose when kept coming. Worth noting all three career wins have been with Hurdle aboard and he rides again today. Top prospects. EDZEL (3) is another who is better than recent form suggests. Back in grade on last run at Sale when fifth. Gets his chance to find form. DISMOUNT (7) was a winner three back but disappointing since. Back in class on latest and does go very well here but will need some luck from the gate. SAWBAY (8) ran a much better race second-up and is a third-up winner and also won only other try here. Should be ready.
